{"title":"Desert Flowers | Daniel Gibson","link":"https://theradavist.com/desert-flowers-daniel-gibson/","date":1739894437000,"content":"<p><em>Painter <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hotburrrito1/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Daniel Gibson</a> is the subject of <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/santa-cruz-bicycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Santa Cruz Bicycles</a>‘ latest video. Read on for a quick project synopsis and a selection of photographs from LA photographer <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vernor\" target=\"_blank\">Brian Vernor</a> below…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-017.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-017.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-017.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-017.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-016.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-016.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-016.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-016.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>How do you portray struggle and pain in a beautiful, vibrant image?…</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-06.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-06.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-06.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-06.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-07.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-07.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-07.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-07.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>There was a point in Daniel Gibson’s life when he stopped making work that was angry. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-05.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-05.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-05.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-05.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-04.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-04.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-04.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-03.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-03.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-03.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>While discussions about political issues often use imagery that has a fist in the air or chainlink fences breaking, Daniel’s work is different. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-02.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-02.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-01.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-01.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-01.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Born in Yuma, AZ and growing up in El Centro, CA with parents who immigrated from Mexico, Daniel Gibson’s early years were spent wrestling with harsh realities of migration to America. </p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-014.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-014.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-014.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-014.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-011.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-011.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-011.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-011.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-013.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-013.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-013.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/02/Desert-Flowers-Daniel-Gibson-013.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>His art brings to life the surreal narratives and questions that captivated him as a child. </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/desert-flowers-daniel-gibson/\">Desert Flowers | Daniel Gibson</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"15a51b06c30b9ec82c86d58b407ba54b1943211157d2727581a7caf0c0b28130","category":"Cycling"}